r Hot reload. 
R Hot restart.
h List all available interactive commands.
d Detach (terminate "flutter run" but leave application running).
c Clear the screen
q Quit (terminate the application on the device).

# 1. Boot the emulator (or start it from Android Studio's Device Manager)
flutter emulators --launch Pixel_7

# 2. Wait ~30–60s for it to boot, then confirm Flutter sees it
flutter devices

# 3. Run the app on it (the device id is usually emulator-5554)
flutter run -d emulator-5554